text: Higeno anante kini ne'mo'a ru'ene mago sondia ne' huntegeno hosi afu agumpi manino vuno, Jehu nagara ome nezamageno anage hu'ne, Kini ne'mo'a huno tamagra ha' eritma neazafi tamarimpa frune neaze hu'ne. Anagema nehiana Jehu'a asmino, Rimpa fruma huno mani'zana kagriza omne'neanki tamefi eramage antenka eno.
